            "title": "Standing Hip Adduction Stretch Instructions",
            "content": {
                "type": "steps",
                "items": [
                    "Stand with your feet hip-width apart and your hands on your hips.",
                    "Lift your right leg off the ground and bring it across your body, placing your right ankle on your left thigh.",
                    "Slowly lower your body down towards your left leg, keeping your back straight and your hips level.",
                    "Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, feeling a stretch in your right hip.",
                    "Slowly return to the starting position and repeat on the other side."
                ]
            }
        },
